name: Global Webinar on Biosensors and Bioelectronics
content: Fratun Meetings extends you the enormous pleasure and the honor of inviting you to attend Global Webinar on Biosensors and Bioelectronics ( GWBB-2022 ) which will be held during 03-04, March 2022\. The theme of the virtual event is “Novel Innovations and Researches in the field of Biosensor and Bioelectronics Technologies”. The main intention behind the GWBB-2022 is to bring together renowned doctors, scientists, researchers, and scholars from all over the world to exchange their ideas, to present sophisticated research works, and to discuss the latest advancements in the field of Global Webinar on Biosensors and Bioelectronics.
